  <brief_title>The Use of Sunscreen Starting on the First Day After Ablative Fractional Skin Resurfacing</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Use of Sunscreen Starting on the First Day After Ablative Fractional Skin Resurfacing - A Pilot Study.</official_title>
